talled · enabled · running (pid 12046, state active)                               │\n│ Node service         │ systemd not installed                                                                         │\n│ Agents               │ 2 · 2 bootstrap files present · sessions 17 · default main active just now                    │\n│ Memory               │ 0 files · 0 chunks · dirty · sources memory · plugin memory-core · vector unknown · fts       │\n│                      │ ready · cache on (0)                                                                          │\n│ Plugin compatibility │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Probes               │ skipped (use --deep)                                                                          │\n│ Events               │ none                                                                                          │\n│ Tasks                │ 2 active · 0 queued · 2 running · no issues · audit 2 errors · 2 warn · 4 tracked             │\n│ Heartbeat            │ 30m (main), disabled (tts)                                                                    │\n│ Sessions             │ 17 active · default MiniMax-M2.7 (200k ctx) · 2 stores                                        │\n└──────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nTask maintenance: openclaw tasks maintenance --apply\n\nSecurity audit\nSummary: 0 critical · 3 warn · 1 info\n  WARN Gateway token looks short\n    gateway auth token is 12 chars; prefer a long random token.\n  WARN Some gateway.nodes.denyCommands entries are ineffective\n    gateway.nodes.denyCommands uses exact node command-name matching only (for example `system.run`), not shell-text filtering inside a command payload. - Unknown …\n    Fix: Use exact command names (for example: canvas.present, canvas.hide, canvas.navigate, canvas.eval, canvas.snapshot, canvas.