{"type":"message","id":"3706ac43","parentId":"8d0c0e26","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:34:47.157Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clearer picture. Let me summarize:\n\n1. **memory-core** - the built-in core memory system (file-based, handles MEMORY.md and memory/*.md)\n2. **memory-lancedb** - vector database for semantic search of memory (with OpenAI embeddings)\n3. **openviking** - a remote plugin pointing to localhost:1933, acts as a context engine\n\nSo the three memory systems are:\n1. **短期/中期/长期记忆** → memory-core (files: MEMORY.md + memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md)\n2. **语义搜索记忆** → memory-lancedb (vector database with embeddings)\n\n\n3. **OpenViking** → context engine running remotely at localhost:1933\n\nThe `memory_search` tool I use leverages both lancedb for semantic vector search and memory-core for the file-based retrieval. OpenViking is distinct from these—it's the context engine that orchestrates recall and capture during the prompt lifecycle. So I can now give a complete breakdown of how each system works and what it handles."},{"type":"text","text":"搞清楚了，4.12 的记忆是**三层并存**：\n\n| 层 | 技术 | 存储位置 | 作用 |\n|----|------|---------|------|\n| **文件记忆** | memory-core | `MEMORY.md` + `memory/*.md` | 人工维护的长期记忆 |\n| **向量记忆** | memory-lancedb | `~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb-pro/` | 语义搜索（用 OpenAI embeddings 建索引） |\n| **上下文引擎** | OpenViking | 远程服务 localhost:1933 | auto-recall/auto-capture，对话级上下文管理 |\n\n`memory_search` 工具会同时查 **lancedb 向量库** 和 **文件记忆** 两边。\n\nOpenViking 是作为独立 context-engine 插件接入的，跟前两层不一样——它管的是\"对话过程中实时 recall/capture\"。\n\n简单说：文件记忆是人工写的，向量记忆是自动索引的，OpenViking 是对话级别的上下文管道。三者各司其职。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776159270537,"responseId":"062d3d2732bcdf64a0b2ed97ad7690a7"}}
