{"type":"message","id":"05cfb8ed","parentId":"3dc6dea3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:36:26.280Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue clearly. The \"选品专家\" subagent spawned at 1774598839871 (April 9, 2026 around 21:47 CST) was given the task \"选品专家，快速筛选市场潜力产品\". It immediately failed with a 402 credit error on OpenRouter (openrouter/auto model), then retried successfully.\n\nThe problem: **Each subagent session is isolated**. When this subagent was spawned, it:\n1. Started fresh with no memory of previous sessions\n2. The model used is `openrouter/auto` (free tier) which has credit issues\n\n\n3. It doesn't have access to the MEMORY.md or the established context from our main session, so it asked the user the same questions from scratch again instead of leveraging what we already discussed.\n\nThis is the classic subagent memory problem—they're disconnected from the main agent's context and can't access long-term memory files unless explicitly configured to do so. I should report this diagnosis back to the user."},{"type":"text","text":"找到根本原因了。\n\n**问题诊断：**\n\n选品 Agent（`35a36f61`）在 4 月 9 日 21:47 被 spawn 后，立刻问了用户一模一样的问题——\"目标品类是什么、市场是哪个\"——而这些本应是之前对话中已经对齐过的内容。\n\n也就是说，每次 spawn 出来的是一个**从零开始的 fresh session**，不继承主对话的任何记忆。\n\n**三个原因导致\"记不住\"：**\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **隔离会话** | 子 Agent 每次 spawn 独立，不带上下文 |\n| **模型限制** | 部分用了 `openrouter/auto`（免费层，有 402 额度限制） |\n| **无持久化记忆** | 子 Agent 不读 MEMORY.md，也不写 memory/ |\n\n这批 subagent 都是\"一次性\"任务型——跑完就结束，不留记忆。想要有记忆的选品 Agent，需要用带记忆的 session 模式，而不是跑完就结束的 run 模式。\n\n要我帮你把选品 Agent 改成持久 session 模式吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776159364612,"responseId":"062d3d85dca807e77240f150188fc238"}}
