{"type":"message","id":"45a48cde","parentId":"9d0e0a8c","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:42:26.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has two requests:\n1. Fix the subagents to have memory like the main agent - so that when they talk to me or any subagent, the context is shared\n2. Understand why they're always getting \"Something went wrong\" errors\n\nLet me tackle both. First, let me understand the current architecture for how subagents are spawned and whether there's a way to share memory. \n\nThe issue with subagents not remembering is that:\n1. They're spawned as one-shot `run` mode sessions\n2. They don't have access to the main session's conversation history\n3. They don't read MEMORY.md or memory files\n\nFor the \"Something went wrong\" error - I need to figure out where this is coming from. It could be from the Feishu channel, or from OpenClaw itself.\n \nLooking at the `sessions_spawn` call, I can see it uses `mode: \"run\"` which creates isolated sessions that terminate after completion. To enable memory sharing, I'd need to switch to `mode: \"session\"` so the subagent maintains its own persistent context, or implement a mechanism to pass conversation history to the subagent.\n\nThe architecture would benefit from a centralized memory store—something like a dedicated file or vector database—that both the main agent and all subagents read from and write to at the start and end of each task. This would be more reliable than trying to share session context directly.\n\nFor the \"Something went wrong\" error, I'm seeing duplicate message IDs which suggests the Feishu channel might be retrying requests or there's an issue with how the bot is handling responses.\n\nLet me start implementing the fix while also investigating the error source."},{"type":"text","text":"好，两个问题一起处理。先查 \"Something went wrong\" 的来源，同时看当前 subagent 是怎么配置的。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7rvhmymtvvp5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"Something went wrong\" ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7rvhmymtvvp5_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/1688-product-search/SKILL.md","limit":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776159728990,"responseId":"062d3ef19faf67912c1400fc1335bc1f"}}
