{"type":"message","id":"94919646","parentId":"653079bd","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:45:39.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tts agent has its own memory files, meaning it has been creating its own daily memory files in workspace-selector. These contain its own session history.\n\nThe issue is that the tts agent and the main KIIT agent don't share memory. When HALEI talks to KIIT about something, and then spawns the tts agent, it doesn't know what was discussed before.\n\nThere are two approaches:\n1. Change tts agent's workspaceDir to `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace` (main workspace) - so it reads/writes the same MEMORY.md and memory/ files\n\n\n2. Keep workspaces separate but ensure memory files are shared/synced\n\nThe simplest approach is option 1: point tts to the main workspace so it accesses the same memory files, though this means it would also read AGENTS.md, USER.md and other main workspace files. Since the tts agent already has `spawnMode: \"session\"`, I just need to update its workspaceDir to the main workspace path.\n\nBut there's a conflict - the tts agent's workspace-selector has its own independent files, so consolidating to the main workspace would break that separation. The real issue is that subagents spawn fresh each time with no memory of previous interactions with the user, unless we explicitly pass context. Making the tts agent persistent and shared could help, but that brings its own complications.\n\nThe most straightforward fix is pointing the tts agent to the main workspace so it shares the same memory files as the main agent - that way when KIIT knows something, the tts agent will know it too. Let me make that change now."},{"type":"text","text":"`tts` 已经是 session 模式，但工作区隔离导致记忆不互通。最简单的方案：把它指向主 workspace。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8sd84az70sqn_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/config.json","edits":[{"oldText":"\"workspaceDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-selector\",","newText":"\"workspaceDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace\","}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776159923819,"responseId":"062d3fb4d3c52e466366178fd43c1a3a"}}
