{"type":"message","id":"787f37b5","parentId":"ab95a5a3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:45:52.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me summarize what I found and fixed for the user:\n\n1. \"Something went wrong\" - likely a Feishu client-side error, not an OpenClaw error\n2. Memory issues - two problems:\n   - product-selector was in \"run\" mode (now changed to \"session\")\n   - tts selector was in \"session\" mode but with isolated workspace (now changed to point to main workspace)\n\nLet me also think about whether there's a way to check the \"Something went wrong\" more. Actually, I should check if there's something in the Feishu plugin config that might cause this. But since I can't find \"Something went wrong\" in the code, it's almost certainly a Feishu client-side message."},{"type":"text","text":"两处都改好了。总结：\n\n**已修复：**\n\n| Agent | 问题 | 修复 |\n|-------|------|------|\n| `product-selector` | `spawnMode: \"run\"` 不留记忆 | → 改为 `\"session\"` |\n| `tts` 选品专家 | 工作区隔离 (`workspace-selector`)，记忆不互通 | → 指向主 workspace |\n\n**\"Something went wrong\"**：\nOpenClaw 代码里搜不到这个字符串——它不是 OpenClaw 报的。大概率是**飞书客户端**在消息送达失败时显示的通用提示（比如网络抖动、token 过期、重发超时等）。你可以留意一下出现时网络是否稳定，或者是否在消息发送失败重试时看到。\n\n**注意**：修改后需要**新的对话**才能用上新配置——已经在跑的 session 不受影响。下次 spawn 选品 Agent 时会自动用 session 模式并共享主记忆。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776159939584,"responseId":"062d3fc392aeb214c8f1007e4da3feae"}}
