{"type":"message","id":"ea4c196c","parentId":"1b360dcb","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:49:12.298Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is explaining that the workspace should be organized with separate directories for each agent/function:\n- Workspace/Selector (for product selection)\n- Workspace/Operations (for operations)\n- Workspace/Data Analysis (for data analysis)\n\nAnd each should have its own storage/memory, but they should be able to share context when needed.\n\nSo the \"workspace isolation\" I found for the tts selector agent isn't wrong - it's actually the intended design! Each sub-agent should have its own workspace directory with its own memory, skills, etc.\n\nLet me re-read what they said: they want independent workspaces under Workspace for different functions (Selector, Operations, Data Analysis), each with their own storage. But they also want me (the main agent) to know what happened in previous conversations.\n\n\nI should have separate workspace directories for each function, but I need a way to access and understand what happened in each one. The isolation keeps things clean, but I need to be able to recall past interactions from these separate workspaces when needed."},{"type":"text","text":"明白了。你的意思是：\n\n```\nWorkspace/\n├── 主agent（我 KIIT）\n├── Selector/          ← 选品专用workspace\n├── Operations/        ← 运营专用\n├── DataAnalysis/      ← 数据分析专用\n└── ...\n```\n\n每个子 Agent 有**独立的工作区和存储**，互不污染，但主 agent 要能跨区 recall。\n\n我之前把 `tts` 改回主 workspace 是改错了——应该保持隔离，但需要给每个 workspace 配 `AGENTS.md` + `SOUL.md` 等初始化文件，让它有独立的\"人格\"和记忆区。\n\n现在 `Selector` 已经有一个独立 workspace 在 `workspace-selector/` 里，里面有 memory、skills 等完整结构。我需要做的是：\n\n1. 把它正式命名为 `Selector/`（重目录）\n2. 给其他两个（Operations、DataAnalysis）初始化同样的结构\n3. 确保我 spawn 它们时，指定对的 `workspace` 参数\n\n要我现在就开始初始化吗？还是先确认一下 `Selector` 的结构是否完整再动？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTo