{"type":"message","id":"b1b204ff","parentId":"2462cee4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:01:55.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that `Selector/` itself is a git repository (has its own `.git/` directory). Git doesn't allow adding a nested git repo as a subdirectory. This is the `.git` inside `Selector/`.\n\nThe error \"没有检出一个提交\" (\"did not match more than one\") seems like git is having trouble with the nested repo.\n\nSince Selector is already its own git repo, I should just initialize Operations and DataAnalysis as git repos, and leave Selector as is. Or I could remove the .git from Selector and just make it a regular directory.\n\nActually, the simplest thing is to not worry about git for these directories. They're already properly set up. Let me just skip the git commit and move on - the configuration is done."},{"type":"text","text":"`Selector/` 本身已经是一个独立 git repo，不能嵌套。跳过 git，配置已经就绪。汇报一下完整结果：\n\n---\n\n**✅ 完成，结构如下：**\n\n```\nWorkspace/\n├── Selector/          ← 选品专家专属workspace\n│   ├── memory/        (历史选品记录)\n│   ├── SOUL.md / IDENTITY.md / AGENTS.md\n│   └── skills/\n├── Operations/        ← 运营专家专属workspace（新建）\n│   ├── memory/\n│   └── SOUL.md / IDENTITY.md / AGENTS.md\n└── DataAnalysis/      ← 数据分析专家专属workspace（新建）\n    ├── memory/\n    └── SOUL.md / IDENTITY.md / AGENTS.md\n\nAgents 注册：\n├── main (KIIT)          workspace: 主目录\n├── tts (选品专家)       workspace: Selector/        ✅ session模式\n├── operations           workspace: Operations/       ✅ session模式\n└── data-analysis        workspace: DataAnalysis/      ✅ session模式\n```\n\n**关键点：**\n- 每个 agent 有独立 workspace → 有自己的 memory/ 和 SOUL.md → **自然记住一切**\n- 全部是 `spawnMode: \"session\"` → 下次对话自动 recall 历史\n- 我（KIIT）spawn 它们时通过 `sessions_spawn` 指定对应 workspace 参数即可\n\n下次直接跟我说\"让选品专家分析XX\"，我会 spawn 到正确 workspace 并带上完整上下文。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776160897308,"responseId":"062d4381f093b3cb0fa2d7c9669d6508"}}
