{"type":"message","id":"40b82303","parentId":"6606b453","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:11:52.491Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a thorough picture of what the Selector workspace has in its memory files. Let me now create the MEMORY.md for Selector and also update the AGENTS.md to make sure it loads MEMORY.md like the main agent does.\n\nKey facts from the memory files:\n1. **Business context**: TikTok Shop Southeast Asia hair accessories (发饰) - focused on Thailand (TH) and Vietnam (VN)\n2. **Product categories**: 发夹、发箍、发圈、头绳、抓夹、发簪\n3. **Selection strategy**: EchoTik 新品榜 as primary source, 7-day sales 50-500, uptrend\n\n\n4. **Data sources**: EchoTik for TikTok product data, 1688 official skills for supply chain matching\n5. **Profit calculation**: Thailand margin ≥25%, Vietnam margin ≥20% (formula with exchange rate + markup)\n6. **Hard filters**: Monthly sales <100, weight >200g, rating <4.5\n7. **Workflow**: EchoTik new product leaderboard → product detail (price, SKU, inventory) → 1688 image search → profit calculation → write to Feishu Bitable\n8. **Bitable**: App Token `AKppbAeyXanTo\n\nTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`, Table ID `tblHU2do30jzinJT`\n\nNow I need to set up the MEMORY.md for the Selector workspace and update its AGENTS.md so it loads this file at startup, establishing the same three-tier memory structure the main agent uses."},{"type":"text","text":"清楚了，Selector 里的 memory 文件记录了大量选品上下文。现在建 MEMORY.md，把关键知识固化进去：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8mqa6ov5vo0h_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector/MEMORY.md","content":"# MEMORY.md - 选品专家长期记忆\n\n## 业务定位\n专注 **TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品**，主力市场 **泰国（TH）+ 越南（VN）**，主营品类：发夹、发箍、发圈、头绳、抓夹、发簪。\n\n## 数据源\n- **EchoTik**（echotik.live）：TikTok 商品销量/GMV/达人数据，覆盖 16 个站点\n- **1688 官方 Skill**：供应链查价、同款匹配（需配置 API Key）\n\n## 选品流程（标准操作链）\n1. EchoTik 新品榜（TH + VN）→ 时尚配件 → 发饰子类目（发绳/发带发箍/发夹发簪）\n2. 筛选：7天销量 50-500 + 上升趋势\n3. 点进产品详情 → 看价格区间、SKU规格、库存（库存少=海外仓备货，判断依据）\n4. 1688 图搜同款 → 供应链价格 → 利润率核算\n5. 利润率达标（TH≥25% / VN≥20%）→ 写入飞书 Bitable\n\n## 硬性筛选规则\n- 月销 < 100 单 ❌\n- 重量 > 200g ❌\n- 评分 < 4.5 ❌\n- IP 侵权风险（迪士尼/Sanrio 等）❌\n\n## 利润计算公式\n- 泰国：毛利率 ≥ 25%（汇率 + 加价系数）\n- 越南：毛利率 ≥ 20%（汇率 + 加价系数）\n- 具体系数见当日 memory 文件或 Bitable 配置\n\n## 飞书 Bitable 配置\n- App Token：`AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`\n- Table ID：`tblHU2do30jzinJT`\n- 用于同步选品结果（S/A/B/C 等级推荐）\n\n## 榜单优先级\n| 榜单 | 频率 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 新品榜 | 每天 | 抓起爆苗子（≤90天新上架），命中率最高 |\n| 选品库筛选 | 每天 | 7天/30天销量双向验证，找老品遗珠 |\n| 飙升榜 | 每周 | 看突然起量的品类，做趋势判断 |\n\n## Skill 状态\n- ✅ `linkfox-echotik-product-search`：已安装，可搜索 TikTok 商品\n- ✅ `1688-product-search`：已安装，需配置 API Key 使用\n- `alphashop-sel-product-search`：备用选品\n- `google-trends`：市场趋势参考\n\n## 1688 API 配置（待完成）\n需要申请 1688 开放平台 API Key，配置到 Skill 环境变量：\n- `ALI1688_APP_KEY`\n- `ALI1688_APP_SECRET`\n- `ALI1688_REFRESH_TOKEN`\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776161477499,"responseId":"062d45c58e8ab9b9d489621af294a3a1"}}
