{"type":"message","id":"0f66f6f3","parentId":"deddd64c","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:16:01.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `openviking` plugin registers a context-engine, but:\n1. Port 1933 is not listening (so OpenViking remote service isn't actually running)\n2. Memory shows 0 files, 0 chunks - LanceDB is empty\n3. The plugin is registered in config but isn't doing anything real\n\nSo OpenViking is registered as a context engine but the actual remote service (port 1933) isn't running. It seems like it's a no-op in this setup.\n\nThe key question is: is OpenViking providing any real value, or is it just a dangling registration?\n\nGiven that:\n1. Port 1933 is not listening → OpenViking remote isn't running\n\n\n2. LanceDB shows 0 chunks → nothing indexed\n3. memory-core (file-based) is what's actually working\n\nOpenViking appears to be a leftover registration from when it was previously deployed, now just taking up space. Since the actual value comes from memory-core and the file-based system, removing OpenViking wouldn't hurt—but I should verify whether it's genuinely providing context-engine functionality before recommending removal."},{"type":"text","text":"查清楚了：\n\n**实际情况：**\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| OpenViking 插件注册 | ✅ 注册了（context-engine hook） |\n| OpenViking 远程服务（:1933） | ❌ **端口没监听，根本没跑** |\n| LanceDB | ❌ 0 chunks，完全是空的 |\n| memory-core（文件记忆） | ✅ 真实在工作 |\n\n**结论：OpenViking 现在是空壳。** 它在配置里挂了 context-engine 的钩子，但远程服务根本没启动，所以没有任何实际作用。\n\n4.12 新架构下，真正在用的是：\n- **memory-core**（文件，MEMORY.md + memory/*.md）\n- **memory-lancedb**（向量库，但没索引任何东西，等于没用）\n- **OpenViking**（注册了但没服务，躺着空转）\n\n既然 lancedb 也是空的（0 chunks），那么 OpenViking 和 lancedb 这两个都可以清理掉——它们都是之前架构遗留的\"曾经想用但没用起来\"的东西。\n\n**建议：关掉这两个插件，回归 pure 文件记忆**，更简单、更可控。你觉得呢？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWri